@NODE "MenüDrucken" "Drucken"
@TOC "MAIN"



Print
=====
  If you select this menupoint a window appears, in which you can
  make different settings according to the output of the data`s.
  You have the choice between: Output on a printer, in a file or in
  a window on the screen.

  You should check the layout in a window, before you start the output
  on a printer or on a data medium, that`s saves time and honey*.

  (*Slogan of a german cartoonist named Ulli Stein)

@ENDNODE

@NODE "MenüHauptkategorie" "Hauptkategorie"
@TOC "MAIN"



Maincategory
============

  If you have changed the category, in the meantime. With this menupoint
  you can go to the maincategory (Root).

