@NODE "MenüFensterZoom" "Vergrößerung"
@TOC "MAIN"



Zoom
====

  The zoom window appears.Here you can see the selected stamps
  in larger display. According to the settings the pictures will shown
  whether quick or slowlier but in higher quality. If you use the
  24bit mode you can also enlarge or reduce the size of zoomwindow.
