@NODE "ARexxSelectStamp" "Bild wählen"
@TOC "MAIN"



SelectStamp
===========


description
-----------
  With SelectStamp you can choose a stamp from an already loaded file.
  No errormessage will show, if the stamp could not found.

parameter
---------
