@NODE "GrafikGIF" "GIF Lademodule"
@TOC "MAIN"



GIF
===

Format:
          GIF (Graphics Interchange Format)

supports:
          1-8Bit (1 - 256 colors)

compression:
          LZW (Lempel-Ziv-Welch)

notice:
          The gif-format was original designed for use with data transfer.
          Because it`s LZW-compression makes the file 10-50% smaller,
          so that the data transfer became very faster.
          Today the gif format is wide spread so that no graphic program
          can ignore it. The gif format supports pictures up to 256 colors
          only.

