@NODE "OperatorMain" "Bildbearbeitungsfunktionen"
@TOC "MAIN"



                  pictureprocessing functions
                  ===========================

  ArtStudio supports a lot of powerful pictureprocessing functions,
  which allows you to manipulate a pictures like you want.
  We have optimate the pictureprossecing functions. Now they work
  very quick and efficient.

  Here, you can see a list of the availble functions. In the future
  you can get further picture processing modules from the Aminet
  or as a update. We will write to registered user if a update is coming
  up. Also see section "future"




